Summarizing is NOT:

```text id="r7s5qe"
copying
every
sentence
```

Students learn:

```text id="x2s8qe"
read carefully
→ identify important ideas
→ remove unnecessary details
→ combine key information
→ express gist
```

This develops:

* comprehension
* synthesis
* organization
* concise communication
* critical reading

